Dialing up cheap data in India

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
India's telecoms giant, Reliance, is offering smartphone users what it says is the cheapest mobile data in the world.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
5 September 2016 Last updated at 01:54 BST
It's hoping to tap into India's vast market of potential smartphone users.
Shilpa Kannan reports from Delhi.
